Format for config.txt:
    number of layers (2 to 4)
    number of input neurons
    number of hidden layer 1 neurons
    number of hidden layer 2 neurons
    number of output neurons

Format for weights.txt:
    for layer in [hidden1, hidden2, output]:
        for neuron in layer:
            for weight in neuron:
                weight
            bias

zero_hidden:
    activation function: None
    accuracy: about 95%
one_hidden:
    activation function: sigmoid
        (ref: https://www.tensorflow.org/versions/r0.10/api_docs/python/nn/activation_functions_#sigmoid)
    accuracy: about 41%

